shelp screen
How to use the screen utility

   create a named screen:
     screen -S myscreen

   list all screens:
     screen -list

   attach a screen:
     screen -r myscreen

   Other useful options:
     -S: specify a screen by name
     -X: send the specified command to the named screen.
         You can also use -d or -r to only look for attached or detached
         screens
   
   From inside a screen:
     quit: quits the screen
   
   So to kill a screen:
     screen -X -S screenName quit

   To remotely detach a screen
     screen -d screenName